    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/cou2-vad-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD hemolysis model is accepted for the VAD context of use. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification provides sufficient confidence in the hemolysis index predictions, and the overall weight of evidence across assessed factors supports regulatory submission. Factors with achieved levels below required levels are acknowledged as areas for future improvement but are not considered disqualifying given the conservative clinical threshold margin observed in validation results.",
